<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>新闻中心</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/news/news.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="headMask"></div>
    <header>
        <div class="header-wrap">
            <ul class="header-nav">
                <li class="h1"><a href="/" class="header-nav-list">首页<div class="border"></div></a></li>
                <li class="h3"><a href="/news" class="header-nav-list header-nav-active">酉阳资讯<div class="border"></div></a></li>
                <li class="h2"><a href="/play" class="header-nav-list">玩转酉阳<div class="border"></div></a></li>
                <li class="h4"><a href="/hotel" class="header-nav-list">酉阳酒店<div class="border"></div></a></li>
                <% if(userType == 'admin') { %>
                <li class="h5"><a href="/admin" class="header-nav-list">管理中心<div class="border"></div></a></li>
                 <% } %>
            </ul>
            <% if(!username) { %>
                <div class="login-out">
                    <a href="/login" id="login">登录</a>
                    <span>|</span>
                    <a href="/regist" id="regist">注册</a>
                </div>
            <% } else { %> 
                <div class="login-haved">
                    <p><a href="/user/center">用户：<%=username%></a></p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="useless"></div>
    <div class="content1">
        <div class="subShadowBox"></div>
        <div class="content1-in">
            <div class="content-left">
                <div class="melon-center"><div class="melon"></div><div class="melon"></div></div>
                <div class="melon-box">
                    <h2>酉阳印象</h2>
                    <p>酉阳土家族苗族自治县位于重庆市境东南部，是重庆市幅员面积最广、少数民族人口最多的县。北临黔江区，西北邻彭水苗族土家族自治县，西隔乌江与贵州省相望，东南与秀山土家族苗族自治县毗邻，东界湖南省，东北邻湖北省，是出渝达鄂湘黔的重要门户，素有“渝东南门户、湘黔咽喉”之称。境内生态环境十分优越，享有“天然氧吧”、“动植物王国”的美誉。境内旅游资源丰富，景点众多。有桃花源国家5A级旅游景区、“小桂林”酉水河景区等自然景观，也有国家级历史文化名镇龙潭古镇、龚滩古镇。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-right">
                <div class="news-center"><div class="egg"></div><h2>新闻资讯</h2><div class="egg"></div></div>
                <ul class="box">
                    <% for (let i = 0; i < article.length; i ++) { %>
                        <li class="item">
                            <a href="/news/<%=article[i].id %>">
                                <div class="title"><%=article[i].article_name %></div>
                                <div class="item-info">
                                    <img src="/img/news/<%=article[i].article_pics %>" alt="">
                                    <div class="item-content">
                                        <p class="item-news-cont"><%=article[i].article_detail %></p>
                                        <div class="item-time"><%=article[i].article_time %></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>

                </ul>
                <div class="load">加载更多</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/news/news.js"></script>
</body>
</html>